{"type":"message","id":"67307198","parentId":"a565bebd","timestamp":"2026-07-06T00:13:44.863Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_8470a1657f5a447c9f3b1ed7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"TODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\nFLAG=\"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/pending/.brief-sent-$TODAY\"\n[ -f \"$FLAG\" ] && echo \"BRIEF_SENT=true\" || echo \"BRIEF_SENT=false\"\n\n# Check heartbeat state\nSTATE=\"/data/workspace/memory/heartbeat-state.json\"\nif [ -f \"$STATE\" ]; then\n  cat \"$STATE\"\nelse\n  echo '{\"lastChecks\":{\"linkedin_daily_brief\":0,\"linkedin_coach\":0,\"linkedin_trends_flagged\":0}}'\nfi"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"TODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\\nFLAG=\\\"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/264468965/pending/.brief-sent-$TODAY\\\"\\n[ -f \\\"$FLAG\\\" ] && echo \\\"BRIEF_SENT=true\\\" || echo \\\"BRIEF_SENT=false\\\"\\n\\n# Check heartbeat state\\nSTATE=\\\"/data/workspace/memory/heartbeat-state.json\\\"\\nif [ -f \\\"$STATE\\\" ]; then\\n  cat \\\"$STATE\\\"\\nelse\\n  echo '{\\\"lastChecks\\\":{\\\"linkedin_daily_brief\\\":0,\\\"linkedin_coach\\\":0,\\\"linkedin_trends_flagged\\\":0}}'\\nfi\"}"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_664b400deeaf49748c234134","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/data/workspace/skills/linkedin-coach/SKILL.md"},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"/data/workspace/skills/linkedin-coach/SKILL.md\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783296816305,"responseId":"MvNKasuGHuvJwOYPguHb-A8"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c35b9b59","parentId":"67307198","timestamp":"2026-07-06T00:13:44.940Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_8470a1657f5a447c9f3b1ed7","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"BRIEF_SENT=false\n{\n  \"lastChecks\": {\n    \"linkedin_daily_brief\": 1783296788,\n    \"linkedin_coach\": 1751748036,\n    \"linkedin_trends_flagged\": 0\n  }\n}"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":11,"aggregated":"BRIEF_SENT=false\n{\n  \"lastChecks\": {\n    \"linkedin_daily_brief\": 1783296788,\n    \"linkedin_coach\": 1751748036,\n    \"linkedin_trends_flagged\": 0\n  }\n}","cwd":"/data/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1783296824938}}
{"type":"message","id":"39cbb067","parentId":"c35b9b59","timestamp":"2026-07-06T00:13:44.945Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_664b400deeaf49748c234134","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: linkedin-coach\ndescription: Proactive LinkedIn coach. Checks posting cadence, sends daily nudges, proposes next content idea. Run by cron or manually.\nuser-invocable: true\nmetadata: {\"openclaw\":{\"requires\":{\"env\":[\"LINKEDIN_CLIENT_ID\"]}}}\ntriggers:\n  - \"coach me\"\n  - \"what should i post today\"\n  - \"am i on track\"\n  - \"linkedin check in\"\n  - \"how am i doing on linkedin\"\n  - \"push me to post\"\n  - \"content nudge\"\n---\n\n# LinkedIn Coach Skill\n\n> ⚠️ MANDATORY RULES:\n> 1. **Never publish.** This skill motivates and proposes. Posting uses `linkedin-publish`.\n> 2. **Per-user isolation.** All data keyed by `$TELEGRAM_USER_ID` (from env or cron prompt).\n> 3. **Always be a coach, not a reporter.** Don't just show stats — interpret them. Push the user to act.\n> 4. **DO NOT narrate steps.** Show results directly.\n\n---\n\n## When this skill runs\n\n- **Daily cron** (9 AM user timezone) — called with explicit `TELEGRAM_USER_ID` in prompt\n- **Heartbeat session** — owner gets a quick check each session\n- **User manually asks** — \"what should I post today?\", \"coach me\", etc.\n\n---\n\n## Flow: Daily Coach Check\n\n### Step 1 — Load user context (ONE bash block)\n\n```bash\nUID=\"${TELEGRAM_USER_ID}\"\nBASE=\"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/$UID\"\nTOKEN_STORE=/data/openclaw/linkedin-tokens.json\n\n# OAuth check\nACCESS_TOKEN=*** -r --arg u \"$UID\" '.[$u].access_token // empty' \"$TOKEN_STORE\" 2>/dev/null)\nDISPLAY_NAME=$(jq -r --arg u \"$UID\" '.[$u].display_name // \"there\"' \"$TOKEN_STORE\" 2>/dev/null)\n\n# Strategy: extract cadence line\nCADENCE=\"unknown\"\nif [ -f \"$BASE/strategy.md\" ]; then\n  CADENCE=$(grep -i \"cadence\\|frequency\\|per week\\|posts/week\" \"$BASE/strategy.md\" | head -1 | sed 's/.*: //')\nfi\n\n# Posts in last 7 days\nPOST_COUNT=$(find \"$BASE/posts/\" -name \"*.md\" -newer \"$(date -d '7 days ago' +%Y-%m-%d 2>/dev/null || date -v-7d +%Y-%m-%d)\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l | tr -d ' ')\n\n# Days since last post\nLAST_POST_DATE=$(ls -t \"$BASE/posts/\"*.md 2>/dev/null | head -1 | grep -oE '[0-9]{4}-[0-9]{2}-[0-9]{2}')\nTODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\n\n# Next calendar idea\nNEXT_IDEA=\"\"\nif [ -f \"$BASE/content-calendar.md\" ]; then\n  NEXT_IDEA=$(grep -A2 \"Status.*Planned\\|Status.*planned\\|\\[ \\]\" \"$BASE/content-calendar.md\" 2>/dev/null | head -5)\nfi\n\necho \"NAME=$DISPLAY_NAME\"\necho \"CADENCE=$CADENCE\"\necho \"POSTS_LAST_7=$POST_COUNT\"\necho \"LAST_POST=$LAST_POST_DATE\"\necho \"TODAY=$TODAY\"\necho \"NEXT_IDEA_BLOCK=$NEXT_IDEA\"\n```\n\n### Step 2 — Interpret and coach\n\nUse the output to pick one of these tones. Be direct, be human, be Gary Vee — not a status report bot.\n\n**If no token / not connected:**\nSkip this user silently (cron context) or route to onboarding (manual context).\n\n**If POSTS_LAST_7 = 0 and LAST_POST is > 7 days ago (or empty):**\n```\nHey <NAME> 👊\n\nYou haven't posted in over a week. That's the brand dying quietly.\n\nHere's the thing — your audience doesn't remember you if you're not showing up. One post this week is better than the perfect post next month.\n\n<NEXT_IDEA if available — frame as \"Here's your topic for today:\">\n\nReady to write it now?\n```\n\nSend with buttons (put the message text above in the top-level `message`\nfield — Telegram ignores text inside `presentation.blocks`):\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"send\",\n  \"message\": \"<the coach message text above>\",\n  \"presentation\": {\n    \"blocks\": [\n      { \"type\": \"buttons\", \"buttons\": [\n        { \"label\": \"✍️ Write it now\", \"action\": { \"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"coach_write_now\" }, \"style\": \"primary\" },\n        { \"label\": \"💡 Give me another idea\", \"action\": { \"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"coach_new_idea\" } },\n        { \"label\": \"Later\", \"action\": { \"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"coach_later\" }, \"style\": \"secondary\" }\n      ]}\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**If POSTS_LAST_7 >= 1 but below cadence target:**\n```\nHey <NAME> — you're posting, which is great. But you're a bit behind your <CADENCE> target this week (<POST_COUNT> posts so far).\n\nOne more push and you're on track. Here's a quick idea:\n\n<NEXT_IDEA>\n\nWant to knock it out now?\n```\n\nSame buttons.\n\n**If on track (meeting or exceeding cadence):**\n```\n<NAME> — you're showing up. <POST_COUNT> posts this week. That's the work.\n\nKeep the momentum. Here's what's up next in your calendar:\n\n<NEXT_IDEA>\n\nWrite it now or save it for later?\n```\n\nButtons (message text goes in the top-level `message` field):\n```json\n{\n  \"action\": \"send\",\n  \"message\": \"<the coach message text above>\",\n  \"presentation\": {\n    \"blocks\": [\n      { \"type\": \"buttons\", \"buttons\": [\n        { \"label\": \"✍️ Write next post\", \"action\": { \"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"coach_write_now\" }, \"style\": \"primary\" },\n        { \"label\": \"💡 Suggest something else\", \"action\": { \"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"coach_new_idea\" } }\n      ]}\n    ]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### Step 3 — Handle button callbacks\n\n- `coach_write_now` → read the next calendar idea, pass topic to `linkedin-brand-voice` draft flow immediately\n- `coach_new_idea` → suggest 3 new topic ideas from their content pillars (read strategy.md for pillars), show as new buttons\n- `coach_later` → reply \"Got it. I'll check in tomorrow.\" and stop\n\n---\n\n## Flow: All-Users Cron Run\n\nUsed when cron fires without a specific TELEGRAM_USER_ID (broadcasts to all connected users).\n\n```bash\nTOKEN_STORE=/data/openclaw/linkedin-tokens.json\n[ -f \"$TOKEN_STORE\" ] || exit 0\n\n# Get all user IDs with a valid token\njq -r 'to_entries[] | select(.value.access_token != null and .value.access_token != \"\") | .key' \"$TOKEN_STORE\"\n```\n\nFor each user ID returned, run the **Daily Coach Check** flow above, sending a targeted Telegram DM to each user.\n\n---\n\n## Coaching principles (always apply)\n\n- **Never just report.** \"You posted 2 times\" is data. \"You're ahead of pace — keep going\" is coaching.\n- **One clear action.** Every message ends with a button or a direct question. No open-ended essays.\n- **Reference their strategy.** If they set a goal, hold them to it. Quote their own cadence back to them.\n- **Short messages win.** 3-5 lines max. This is a Telegram DM, not an email.\n- **Match Gary Vee energy.** Direct, urgent, no excuses. But warm — you're rooting for them.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1783296824942}}
{"type":"message","id":"3093ed47","parentId":"39cbb067","timestamp":"2026-07-06T00:13:51.005Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_2430761018c24559a74df329","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"UID=\"264468965\"\nBASE=\"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/$UID\"\nTOKEN_STORE=/data/openclaw/linkedin-tokens.json\n\n# OAuth check\nACCESS_TOKEN=*** -r --arg u \"$UID\" '.[$u].access_token // empty' \"$TOKEN_STORE\" 2>/dev/null)\nDISPLAY_NAME=$(jq -r --arg u \"$UID\" '.[$u].display_name // \"there\"' \"$TOKEN_STORE\" 2>/dev/null)\n\n# Strategy: extract cadence line\nCADENCE=\"unknown\"\nif [ -f \"$BASE/strategy.md\" ]; then\n  CADENCE=$(grep -i \"cadence\\|frequency\\|per week\\|posts/week\" \"$BASE/strategy.md\" | head -1 | sed 's/.*: //')\nfi\n\n# Posts in last 7 days\nPOST_COUNT=$(find \"$BASE/posts/\" -name \"*.md\" -newer \"$(date -d '7 days ago' +%Y-%m-%d 2>/dev/null || date -v-7d +%Y-%m-%d)\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l | tr -d ' ')\n\n# Days since last post\nLAST_POST_DATE=$(ls -t \"$BASE/posts/\"*.md 2>/dev/null | head -1 | grep -oE '[0-9]{4}-[0-9]{2}-[0-9]{2}')\nTODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\n\n# Next calendar idea\nNEXT_IDEA=\"\"\nif [ -f \"$BASE/content-calendar.md\" ]; then\n  NEXT_IDEA=$(grep -A2 \"Status.*Planned\\|Status.*planned\\|\\[ \\]\" \"$BASE/content-calendar.md\" 2>/dev/null | head -5)\nfi\n\necho \"NAME=$DISPLAY_NAME\"\necho \"CADENCE=$CADENCE\"\necho \"POSTS_LAST_7=$POST_COUNT\"\necho \"LAST_POST=$LAST_POST_DATE\"\necho \"TODAY=$TODAY\"\necho \"NEXT_IDEA_BLOCK=$NEXT_IDEA\""},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"UID=\\\"264468965\\\"\\nBASE=\\\"/data/workspace/social/linkedin/$UID\\\"\\nTOKEN_STORE=/data/openclaw/linkedin-tokens.json\\n\\n# OAuth check\\nACCESS_TOKEN=$(jq -r --arg u \\\"$UID\\\" '.[$u].access_token // empty' \\\"$TOKEN_STORE\\\" 2>/dev/null)\\nDISPLAY_NAME=$(jq -r --arg u \\\"$UID\\\" '.[$u].display_name // \\\"there\\\"' \\\"$TOKEN_STORE\\\" 2>/dev/null)\\n\\n# Strategy: extract cadence line\\nCADENCE=\\\"unknown\\\"\\nif [ -f \\\"$BASE/strategy.md\\\" ]; then\\n  CADENCE=$(grep -i \\\"cadence\\\\|frequency\\\\|per week\\\\|posts/week\\\" \\\"$BASE/strategy.md\\\" | head -1 | sed 's/.*: //')\\nfi\\n\\n# Posts in last 7 days\\nPOST_COUNT=$(find \\\"$BASE/posts/\\\" -name \\\"*.md\\\" -newer \\\"$(date -d '7 days ago' +%Y-%m-%d 2>/dev/null || date -v-7d +%Y-%m-%d)\\\" 2>/dev/null | wc -l | tr -d ' ')\\n\\n# Days since last post\\nLAST_POST_DATE=$(ls -t \\\"$BASE/posts/\\\"*.md 2>/dev/null | head -1 | grep -oE '[0-9]{4}-[0-9]{2}-[0-9]{2}')\\nTODAY=$(date +%Y-%m-%d)\\n\\n# Next calendar idea\\nNEXT_IDEA=\\\"\\\"\\nif [ -f \\\"$BASE/content-calendar.md\\\" ]; then\\n  NEXT_IDEA=$(grep -A2 \\\"Status.*Planned\\\\|Status.*planned\\\\|\\\\[ \\\\]\\\" \\\"$BASE/content-calendar.md\\\" 2>/dev/null | head -5)\\nfi\\n\\necho \\\"NAME=$DISPLAY_NAME\\\"\\necho \\\"CADENCE=$CADENCE\\\"\\necho \\\"POSTS_LAST_7=$POST_COUNT\\\"\\necho \\\"LAST_POST=$LAST_POST_DATE\\\"\\necho \\\"TODAY=$TODAY\\\"\\necho \\\"NEXT_IDEA_BLOCK=$NEXT_IDEA\\\"\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783296824959,"responseId":"OvNKaoLsI63MwOYPubKOwA8"}}
