{"type":"message","id":"4d0f6121","parentId":"51fff2f2","timestamp":"2026-07-06T00:45:09.685Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_a1818c367776484eb9c7398f","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"📝 Post 3/3 — Personal development & mindset\n\n𝗧𝗵𝗲 𝗴𝗮𝗽 𝗯𝗲𝘁𝘄𝗲𝗲𝗻 𝘄𝗵𝗲𝗿𝗲 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝗮𝗿𝗲 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝘄𝗵𝗲𝗿𝗲 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝘄𝗮𝗻𝘁 𝘁𝗼 𝗯𝗲 𝗶𝘀 𝗻𝗼𝘁 𝗮 𝗹𝗮𝗰𝗸 𝗼𝗳 𝗸𝗻𝗼𝘄𝗹𝗲𝗱𝗴𝗲.\n\nIt's a lack of reps.\n\nWe consume content, read books, take courses, follow thought leaders. We KNOW what to do. But knowing isn't doing.\n\nThe difference between the top 1% and everyone else isn't access to information — it's the willingness to be bad at something in public until you're not.\n\n• The writer who publishes daily even when nobody reads\n• The founder who pitches 100 investors to get 1 yes\n• The engineer who ships messy code and refactors later\n\nEvery expert was once a beginner who refused to quit.\n\nThe reps are free. The discomfort is the price.\n\nWhat are you putting off because you're \"not ready yet\"?\n\n#PersonalDevelopment #Growth #Mindset #Habits #Success\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━\nSource: Evergreen (deliberate practice)","presentation":{"blocks":[{"type":"buttons","buttons":[{"label":"✅ Publish now","action":{"type":"callback","value":"brief_approve_2026-07-06-3"},"style":"success"},{"label":"✏️ Edit first","action":{"type":"callback","value":"brief_edit_2026-07-06-3"}},{"label":"⏭️ Skip","action":{"type":"callback","value":"brief_skip_2026-07-06-3"},"style":"secondary"}]}]}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"send\", \"message\": \"📝 Post 3/3 — Personal development & mindset\\n\\n𝗧𝗵𝗲 𝗴𝗮𝗽 𝗯𝗲𝘁𝘄𝗲𝗲𝗻 𝘄𝗵𝗲𝗿𝗲 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝗮𝗿𝗲 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝘄𝗵𝗲𝗿𝗲 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝘄𝗮𝗻𝘁 𝘁𝗼 𝗯𝗲 𝗶𝘀 𝗻𝗼𝘁 𝗮 𝗹𝗮𝗰𝗸 𝗼𝗳 𝗸𝗻𝗼𝘄𝗹𝗲𝗱𝗴𝗲.\\n\\nIt's a lack of reps.\\n\\nWe consume content, read books, take courses, follow thought leaders. We KNOW what to do. But knowing isn't doing.\\n\\nThe difference between the top 1% and everyone else isn't access to information — it's the willingness to be bad at something in public until you're not.\\n\\n• The writer who publishes daily even when nobody reads\\n• The founder who pitches 100 investors to get 1 yes\\n• The engineer who ships messy code and refactors later\\n\\nEvery expert was once a beginner who refused to quit.\\n\\nThe reps are free. The discomfort is the price.\\n\\nWhat are you putting off because you're \\\"not ready yet\\\"?\\n\\n#PersonalDevelopment #Growth #Mindset #Habits #Success\\n\\n━━━━━━━━━━━\\nSource: Evergreen (deliberate practice)\", \"presentation\": {\"blocks\": [{\"type\": \"buttons\", \"buttons\": [{\"label\": \"✅ Publish now\", \"action\": {\"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"brief_approve_2026-07-06-3\"}, \"style\": \"success\"}, {\"label\": \"✏️ Edit first\", \"action\": {\"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"brief_edit_2026-07-06-3\"}}, {\"label\": \"⏭️ Skip\", \"action\": {\"type\": \"callback\", \"value\": \"brief_skip_2026-07-06-3\"}, \"style\": \"secondary\"}]}]}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"litellm","model":"vertex_ai/zai-org/glm-5-maas","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1783298701883,"responseId":"j_pKapfBHsfKwOYP6KGRmAY"}}
{"type":"message","id":"c3a8b853-36e0-49fb-b0b3-f6f230eb6bb4","parentId":"4d0f6121","timestamp":"2026-07-06T00:45:09.941Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"📝 Post 3/3 — Personal development & mindset\n\n𝗧𝗵𝗲 𝗴𝗮𝗽 𝗯𝗲𝘁𝘄𝗲𝗲𝗻 𝘄𝗵𝗲𝗿𝗲 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝗮𝗿𝗲 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝘄𝗵𝗲𝗿𝗲 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝘄𝗮𝗻𝘁 𝘁𝗼 𝗯𝗲 𝗶𝘀 𝗻𝗼𝘁 𝗮 𝗹𝗮𝗰𝗸 𝗼𝗳 𝗸𝗻𝗼𝘄𝗹𝗲𝗱𝗴𝗲.\n\nIt's a lack of reps.\n\nWe consume content, read books, take courses, follow thought leaders. We KNOW what to do. But knowing isn't doing.\n\nThe difference between the top 1% and everyone else isn't access to information — it's the willingness to be bad at something in public until you're not.\n\n• The writer who publishes daily even when nobody reads\n• The founder who pitches 100 investors to get 1 yes\n• The engineer who ships messy code and refactors later\n\nEvery expert was once a beginner who refused to quit.\n\nThe reps are free. The discomfort is the price.\n\nWhat are you putting off because you're \"not ready yet\"?\n\n#PersonalDevelopment #Growth #Mindset #Habits #Success\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━\nSource: Evergreen (deliberate practice)"}],"api":"openai-responses","provider":"openclaw","model":"delivery-mirror","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1783298709922,"idempotencyKey":"5a1350eb-3b7b-4c98-8549-1099fe022d4f:message-tool:D6jRPKuL8Jyw0e91Ws1x22d2:call_a1818c367776484eb9c7398f"}}
